org.apache.juneau.assertions

Class FluentLongAssertion<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.assertions.Assertion
      • org.apache.juneau.assertions.FluentAssertion<R>
        • org.apache.juneau.assertions.FluentLongAssertion<R>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - The return type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LongAssertion

    public class FluentLongAssertion<R>
extends FluentAssertion<R>
    Used for fluent assertion calls against longs.
    Example:

    // Validates the response length isn't too long. client .get(URL) .run() .assertLongHeader("Length").isLessThan(100000);
